<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Refund Needs Attention</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FFF8E7;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #D4AF37;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .alert-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #F59E0B;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .refund-info {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E7 0%, #FAF0E6 100%);
      border: 1px solid #F4D03F;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .refund-info dt {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .refund-info dd {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #D4AF37;
    }
    .message-box {
      background-color: #FEF3C7;
      border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #F5F5DC;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">SureSpot</div>
      <h1 class="title">Refund Needs Attention</h1>
      <div class="alert-badge">Action Required</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>A customer has requested a refund and you need to provide their bank details for the refund to be processed.</p>

      <dl class="refund-info">
        <dt>Transaction Reference</dt>
        <dd><code>{{reference}}</code></dd>

        <dt>Amount</dt>
        <dd class="amount">{{amount}}</dd>

        <dt>Status</dt>
        <dd>{{status}}</dd>

        <dt>Domain</dt>
        <dd>{{domain}}</dd>
      </dl>

      <div class="message-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #92400E;">
          Action Required
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          Log into the admin dashboard to provide the customer's bank details and complete the refund.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>This is an automated notification from the SureSpot backend.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} SureSpot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
